title: The Civilization Of Maxwell Bright
description:
The Civilization of Maxwell Bright   (2005)

Starring: Patrick Warburton, Jennifer Tilly

Director: David Beaird

Synopsis: Male chauvinist Max Bright turns to an Asian mail order bride service, hoping to find a compliant partner who will do whatever he tells her. But what Max gets is an unexpected lesson in life in this moving film about the search for meaning and the power of love.

Runtime: 107 minutes

MPAA Rating: R - for strong language including sexual references, some sexuality and graphic nudity.

Excellent Movie well worth watching.
